## prevent error ## recommended
## (EE) AIGLX error: dlopen of
## /usr/lib/i386-linux-gnu/dri/swrast_dri.so failed (/usr/lib/i386-linux-gnu/dri/swrast_dri.so:
## cannot open shared object file: No such file or directory)
## in /var/log/Xorg.0.log
libgl1-mesa-dri

## 1)
## make dialogs look better, not like Windows 95
## https://forums.whonix.org/t/qubes-whonix-13-0-0-0-7-testers-wanted/2432/8
## 2)
## prevent warning when starting for example iceweasel or Tor Browser from terminal ## recommended
## Gtk-WARNING **: Unable to locate theme engine in module_path: "pixmap",
## https://github.com/QubesOS/qubes-issues/issues/1410
gtk2-engines-pixbuf

